    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Last year, I took a leap and launched my needle felting business online. Starting from zero followers on Facebook, I faced the quiet struggle every new artist knows: How do I show up in a world that doesn’t know I exist? Most groups banned promotions, so I stuck to quietly sharing photos of my work, hoping to connect with people. Deep down, I knew how hard it must’ve been for anyone to entrust a stranger online with something as precious as memorializing a lost pet. I was still figuring out global shipping from Shanghai, my hands trembling with every new DM. But slowly, a few brave souls took a chance on me. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Last year, I took a leap and launched my needle felting business online. Starting from zero followers on Facebook, I faced the quiet struggle every new artist knows: How do I show up in a world that doesn’t know I exist? Most groups banned promotions, so I stuck to quietly sharing photos of my work, hoping to connect with people. Deep down, I knew how hard it must’ve been for anyone to entrust a stranger online with something as precious as memorializing a lost pet. I was still figuring out global shipping from Shanghai, my hands trembling with every new DM. But slowly, a few brave souls took a chance on me. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
  },
