          "plain_text": "March 2025, Britt flew across oceans to meet me. As I handed her their portraits, my throat tightened. There they were: Maxie and Felix, alive in fiber form. In that moment, I realized this craft isn’t just about art—it’s about collapsing distance between hearts.",
          "href": null
